They'll plant fake evidence, they'll put a loaded gun in the hands of an unarmed man they shot to death, they harass minorities, they brutalize people, they deny people their rights, and they lie about all of it in court all the time. They perjure themselves routinely.....but they don't squeal on each other. They're not rats. So take a page from their book but never ever help them! Above all, don't plea bargain by turning in a friend.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbae89948b940bcebf40cbbea37eb33876d45a5","tid":1535841,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"要贏國際輿論就同我入嚟， 人哋根本唔知你哋啲口號up乜鳩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"475028cce236af0bae811f4361ff565821e4738e","tid":1535841,"uid":295033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"不督灰 x 黑警死全家"},{"pid":"e2c4efc489ffa462385b2e1011504ec61994ca19","tid":1535841,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d779288a6754ffd0ef98956025aa339eda7c94b2","tid":1535841,"uid":89046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:59:32.000Z","msg":"I'll tell you what, to all you religious people out there, on judgement day when you see god ask him if you can plea bargain, ask him if you turn in your family will he let you into heaven. You know what he'll say? He'll say go to hell you fucking, squealing prick! Cuz even god hates a rat! You know what Jesus should've done? <strong>He should've beat the shit outta Judas! Just grabbed him by the beard and beat the shit outta him right in front of the other apostles, make an example out of him</strong>:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Judas, you fucking squealing prick, you cock sucker! Do you realize I can turn you into a fucking pillar of salt, into a fucking monkey if I want? How'd you like to be a fucking monkey? <strong>And where's the money? Where's the 30 dollars? Gimme the 30 dollars! I'm buying beer for the rest of these guys cuz they didn't fucking rat on me you prick!</strong>&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBut he didn't do that. You know why? Because he believed in all this goofy love bullshit! But notice something else, he did not plea bargain with the Romans and he didn't squeal on the apostles, he kept his big fucking yap shut and he took what was coming to him. <br />\n<br />\nWe can all learn something from Jesus........even if it's not what we're expecting!"},{"pid":"114bb7a7a498f79de27787c215a567b6e7a7cec0","tid":1535841,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9b7c4be5758fec45e79613c3e178cce976035d","tid":1535841,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3ba4fd0a3d25ba32e9845d59babede59ef8221","tid":1535841,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d44163d514404f20ca04c9700f8c6c7e20176d","tid":1535841,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}